"<html>
<head>
<title> Overview of Leibnitz </title>
</head>

Leibnitz provides the calculator you've always wanted, short of handwriting
recognition.  The major features that it provides are:

<ul>
<li> <a href=jxhelp:THXExprHelp>evaluate expressions</a>
<p>
<li> <a href=jxhelp:THX2DPlotHelp>plot 2D functions</a>
<p>
<li> <a href=jxhelp:THXBaseConvHelp>convert between different bases</a>
     (e.g. hex <-> decimal)
</ul>

For more information about a particular feature, simply click on the underlined text.
To search for a word or phrase, select \"Find...\" from the Search menu, enter the
text, and then select \"Search all sections\" from the Search menu.

</html>"
